you will also need to buy a good speaker to listen with the radio...&nbsp; Cheap one don&#39;t work very well.&nbsp; Radio Shack sell a ham radio speaker that works great.&nbsp; It runs around $25.00 also.&nbsp; Don&#39;t forget to buy a recorder or a miciphone for your cpu to record your seesions.&nbsp; I think recording straight on the cpu is the best way to do it, but almost everybody is going to disagree with me on that subject.&nbsp; Thats the way that I do it, and I didn&#39;t have to go out and buy a recorder for 100 bucks.
&nbsp;
Rees

